{"tid":2290721,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"13歲中国女童疑看了女同學傳的紙仔  被對方持刀捅傷","createTime":"2020-11-18T08:15:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-18T16:21:01.000Z","uid":184679,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"82e5267fdf7d38facf0b51d2c36ac1b3fe86c82b","tid":2290721,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T08:15:20.000Z","msg":"在湖南永州，一名藍山縣的梁女士周三（18日）向內地傳媒反映，自己13歲的侄女，被同班14歲女生持刀捅傷多處。梁女士稱，事發在周一（16日）下午，當時由於學校開例會，課室內沒有老師，自己侄女的同班14歲女孩傳了一張紙條，在課室內傳來傳去，不小心丟到她侄女附近，侄女撿起來看了一下，傳紙仔的女孩就跑過去將紙條搶回去，並叫喊：「看甚麼看？」侄女回答：「看一下也看不得呀又不會死人。」女孩回話：「會死人的」。然後，拿出隨身所帶小刀向她的侄女背部捅了幾刀，侄女起身逃跑，女孩追着又將侄女的手臂劃傷，臉部也受了輕傷。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，受傷女孩父母離異後，跟隨梁女士生活。目前，教育局已經介入調查，具體有待官方通報。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static-stheadline-com.cdn.ampproject.org/i/s/static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20201118/_2020111815454031882.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic-stheadline-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fi%2Fs%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20201118%2F_2020111815454031882.jpg&h=b792ac5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://hd.stheadline. com/news/realtime/chi/1927081/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B-13%E6%AD%B2%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%A9%E7%96%91%E7%9C%8B%E4%BA%86%E5%A5%B3%E5%90%8C%E5%AD%B8%E5%82%B3%E7%9A%84%E7%B4%99%E4%BB%94-%E8%A2%AB%E5%B0%8D%E6%96%B9%E6%8C%81%E5%88%80%E6%8D%85%E5%82%B7</code></pre>"},{"pid":"1e112c42222590b9180edaf48507e1801319cbe3","tid":2290721,"uid":200200,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T08:16:21.000Z","msg":"爭d就可以少一隻蝗蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"780ee00fcfe2e5464065cf6bf1dc70702b3e1ca6","tid":2290721,"uid":47160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T08:16:22.000Z","msg":"隨身帶刀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"917391b5d4554d0297b0e993a67e4102bfcdca1c","tid":2290721,"uid":157793,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime